  "detailed_description": "<strong>Twin Robots</strong> is a 2.5D platformer where you can switch control between two little robots; They have been imprisoned and need to find the way out of each level! You can play alone or with a friend in local co-op multiplayer, so that each player controls one robot.<br><br>You'll be running, jumping &amp; solving puzzles together, but beware: Both robots are battery-powered so they consume energy in <i>everything</i> they do! Watch out for their battery levels! You can also transfer energy from one robot to the other so that both can safely reach the exit. Sharing is caring :-)<br><br><strong>Features:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Strategy thinking: Manage your energy levels through the level so that you can safely reach the exit &amp; charge the last door to open it.<br></li><li>Puzzle solving: some levels require both robots to help eachother in order to solve easy puzzles.<br></li><li>Smooth gameplay: You can adjust the framerate and the overall graphic quality from the config. screen, so it better fits the capabilities of your computer.<br></li><li>Local co-op multiplayer action!<br></li><li>Great controller support!</li></ul>",
